<p>同时在今天，我也给自己准备了一件礼物。</p>

<p><a href="/downloads/image/clarinet/1.jpeg" title="Buffet Crampon Prodige Clarinet " class="fancybox"><img src="/downloads/image/clarinet/1.jpeg" alt="Buffet Crampon Prodige Clarinet " /></a></p>

